title: Drummer Johnathan Blake on Tom Harrell & the 3 Cohens
description:
In this interview done during the Jazz Cruise in 2016, drummer Johnathan Blake talks about performing and recording with both Tom Harrell and the Three Cohens. Blake was performing on the cruise with the Kenny Barron Trio and the Three Cohens.

Interview by Irene Lee.  Video production by Lee Mergner & Melissa Mergner. Thanks to Michael Lazaroff and the production team of Entertainment Cruise Productions. 

For more information about Johnathan Blake, go to www.johnathanblake.com

For more information about the Jazz Cruise, go to www.thejazzcruise.com

For more information about JazzTimes, go to www.jazztimes.com
fulltitle: Drummer Johnathan Blake on Tom Harrell & the 3 Cohens
